<br>
Basically if you are going to avoid being banned for using it then you can't use it to influence your play style, so what's the point again?  Remember Verant can see everything you say and do in game and you have to assume they do log it all.<br>
<br>
In the end, why not install EQ on your second computer and powerlevel a druid to track for you?  Has the added advantage of throwing in heals if you need it...<br>
<br>
As for something being able to tell you WHEN then next spawn will be - can't be done.  Short of knowing when the mob last went down you need inside access to the servers.<br>
